snippet.title: Jim & Dill 2 - Bobson's Revenge (New Original NES Game Trailer)
snippet.description:
Original game for the Nintendo Entertainment System based on the band Weed N' Stiff. 

Physical copies available through Premium Edition (premiumeditiongames.com)

Digital ROM available at:
https://calgames.itch.io

Music by Weed N' Stiff
Original game score by Logan E. Schad.
Coding and Design by calgames

Want to hear more Weed N' Stiff music? Our new album RON is available on every platform (iTunes, Amazon, Spotify, YouTube, etc.) and exclusive material available at:
https://weednstiff.bandcamp.com
